  "Description": {
    "English": "Powerful energy storage unit. Used in a wide variety of <span class=\"name name-commodity\">defensive</span> and <span class=\"name name-commodity\">hazard protection</span> systems.<br><br>Constructed from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Ionized Cobalt</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pure Ferrite</span>, and occasionally found in cylindrical metal containers.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "强大的能量存储单元。在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御系统</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">危险防护系统</span>中有广泛的应用。<br><br>从<span class=\"name name-technology\">电离钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>制作而成，有时可以在圆柱形金属容器中发现。",
    "TencentChinese": "强大的能量存储单元。在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御系统</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">危险防护系统</span>中有广泛的应用。<br><br>从<span class=\"name name-technology\">电离钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>制作而成，有时可以在圆柱形金属容器中发现。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "強力能量儲存單元。廣泛用於<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防禦</span>與<span class=\"name name-commodity\">風險防護</span>系統。<br><br>能以<span class=\"name name-technology\">離子化鈷</span>與<span class=\"name name-earth\">純鐵氧體</span>製成，偶爾能見於圓筒形金屬容器中。"
  },
