  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Advanced Ion Battery from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Ionized Cobalt</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pure Ferrite</span>. Use a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to process advanced materials.<br>Cobalt is found underground. Locate natural cave entrances. <span class=\"name name-red\">WARNING:</span> many caves contain hazardous flora.<br>Supplies are occasionally found in <span class=\"name name-technology\">Supply Caches</span> left on planets.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>制作高级离子电池。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>加工出先进材料。<br>钴能在地下被找到。寻找天然洞穴的入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>许多洞穴中存在危险植物群系。<br>补给品偶尔能从留在行星上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">物资贮存箱</span>中找到。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>制作高级离子电池。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>加工出先进材料。<br>钴能在地下被找到。寻找天然洞穴的入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>许多洞穴中存在危险植物群系。<br>补给品偶尔能从留在行星上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">物资贮存箱</span>中找到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "將<span class=\"name name-technology\">離子化鈷</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">純鐵氧體</span>製作成先進離子電池。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>來處理先進材料。<br>鈷能在地底找到。找出天然洞穴入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>許多洞穴內有危險植物。<br>偶爾能在棄置於星球的<span class=\"name name-technology\">補給儲物箱</span>中找到補給品。"
